data.description:
NO HOA! Great home w/ huge 713 sq ft Air-conditioned & insulated studio/office. Oversized 2-car carport, and there's plenty of storage with two sheds and lots of attic space.
The plumbing in the entire house has been updated in the last two years for peace of mind. You'll love the beach-themed soaking tub.
The master bedroom is spacious, with a bathroom that has two sinks. Both bathrooms have been recently updated for added comfort and style.
Enjoy low electricity bills thanks to the prepaid-for solar system, electricity bills ranging from $80 to $130 in the summer. There are multiple shaded outdoor areas for relaxation & entertainment, including a basketball court & garden. Exterior has been re-painted. Walk to high school. Mountain Views!
